Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是保护联邦市民利益和安全的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  纠正以往错误的政治和军队也是我们军人的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占领了非洲塔低轨道空间站的反政府组织
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发表了犯罪声明以及对联邦议会的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们要求  以解放现空间站内的市民为交换
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解散联邦议会  并释放4万5千名反政府活动者  以及1千…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  联邦政府并没有回应对方的要求  也没有向恐怖分子屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经派遣独立治安维持部队至事发地  以期早日解决事件…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报管制  这些消息都是虚假的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,0:04:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下又能做到些什么？ 哈裘里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基于轨道电梯理论的太阳光发电系统是开创人类未来的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上发生的大多数纷争都是以能源问题为开端的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能解决能源问题的话  粮食  环境等问题都能随之得到解决
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  拥有轨道电梯的国家群正以防卫为名在增强军备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,势均力敌的国家群之间正处于极度紧张状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  将会导致冷战势态…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使是这样  有良知的市民  优异的政治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们军队若能作为此紧张势态的抑制力而正常运转的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会开拓出一条道路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加深彼此的理解  缓和彼此的紧张  进行联合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  世界将会平稳走向统一的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金司令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校  我想交给你一个机密任务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机密任务？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经用正规军包围了低轨道空间站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对地面上的A-LAWS精锐部队发出了派遣命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由正规军发动的政变  如果这一事实被公开的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府运动将会有扩大的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤道环的设置即将完成  我也会上宇宙去指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然放任叛乱分子乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革者在想些什么啊？  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们自有他们的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场政变能改变世界吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道  说不定是终结的开始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是大小姐所期望的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面和这里都被完全包围了  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  跟预期的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔隆那边怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有相当数量的MS正在赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就看Celestial Being会如何行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政变军队对非洲塔的占领
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟卡塔隆的情报一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的撤退也是因为这个理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  该怎么办呢？  皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是去帮忙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革者掌握着吠陀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  为什么他们没有注意到这次的骚乱呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说他们预测到了政变但是任其发生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有这种可能性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  既然动用了A-LAWS  就不会袖手旁观了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  A-LAWS的背后也有改革者存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使他们有所图谋  要知道他们的意图也只能前往事发地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  如果刹那知道了政变的情报的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩  在到达非洲塔之前  武器控制系统能使用么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能这么硬来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS派出了MS队了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个追加装备是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我  我问谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:08:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那些玩神秘的A-LAWS  我们在当前宙域待机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校  是A-LAWS的MS部队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要迎击  让全世界都看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS部队  发射了装载容器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的自动机器人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔离墙壁被突破
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照预定  防卫系统以S模式应对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动机器人的击退概率已达43%
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是进行试探吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校  卡塔隆的部队正在接近支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦的迎击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔隆部队接近支柱发射口  已与我方的地面部队汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面的话也应该部署有A-LAWS的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然他们没有出手的话  就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机体从DH42潜入支柱并在上升
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上显示影像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…铁人桃子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派出MS前去迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理应如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶那台机体的是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照指示  已经派我军的斯米尔诺夫上校作为密使前往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你们的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向A-LAWS调转期间  可以给其将官待遇么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应你  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正规军迟早会被A-LAWS吞并
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是顺应时代的发展吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在当前海域待机？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？  为什么不动用我们这里的部队？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没有我们的出场机会了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此大规模的作战  利冯兹到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在闷闷不乐啊  是因为不能给布林格报仇吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都知道了  我们可是同类哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识叛乱分子的主谋？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是家父的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候听他说过正确的军队的行为什么的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:11:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是居然变成叛乱分子  把6万市民当作人质卷入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟叛乱的理由没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们作为A-LAWS只会与反政府势力作战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了赢取和平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的  准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你真的会来士官学校就读
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您在高层为我进言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不想借用父亲的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参军是为了向你父亲示威吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么恨你父亲  那只是一场不幸的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别说的这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是父亲对母亲见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且您也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会像父亲那样活的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了证明这点才选择成为军人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的认为赫莉会为此而高兴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  因为妈妈比任何人都期望和平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校  不成熟的决心不会带来和平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你不明白现在正是需要A-LAWS的力量呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然来了么  谢尔盖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈裘里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为地球联邦军总司令部的密使通知潘·哈裘里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦政府决不会同意你们的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并劝告政变军尽快投降
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了说这个特意到这里来的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在联邦政府的情报管制已经执行得如此彻底的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的事根本无法让世人知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么把无关的市民作为人质…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是无关
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是这些过着优裕的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对联邦议会的决策毫无疑问就接受的市民们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致的政治堕落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令A-LAWS这样的组织抬头的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也正是市民的愚昧所导致
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须让他们觉醒  即使是伴随着苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:46.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护市民的安全和利益的不正是军人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才在这里这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧  现在还能保住部下的命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为A-LAWS会手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:13:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈裘里…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:14:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈判决裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到地面转告司令部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我们只剩下一个人也决不会离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我留在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我会仅仅因为接到命令就到这里来吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的自动机器人已经侵入了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在前往重力区！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按预定关闭各隔离墙壁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1步兵部队保护线路  把市民护送进列车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2步兵部队负责迎击自动机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈裘里  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动机器人也在攻击市民！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市民中出现死伤！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入的自动机器人是使用杀戮模式的么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了吧  谢尔盖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是错误的政治和军队的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已确保撤退路线  市民正在登上列车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的MS部队好像已经与政变军汇合了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果以此为契机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能将联邦的恶政和A-LAWS的恶行向世界公布的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:43.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有能力进行反抗的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是否能被世界所接受还…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦好像已经发表了官方回应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于答应谈判了么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:16:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线性列车第1班次已经出发  第2班次将于5分钟后发车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从最开始就打算释放市民吗？  但是为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让市民们亲眼目睹联邦政府和A-LAWS的恶行  让他们觉醒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是伴随着苦难…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些苦难将使对联邦政府的质疑化作汹涌波涛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是政治还是军队  只有有良知的市民存在才能正确发挥机能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是为了让他们觉醒  我将很乐意成为弃子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈裘里…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上…上校  联邦的官方回应…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面的影像是独立治安维持部队的无人侦察机\N在非洲塔内部拍摄到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府势力正在夺取空间站内的市民的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦议会正在讨论独立治安维和部队的强行突入…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些影像是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用虚假的情报煽动市民  这是联邦拿手的舆论操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种卑劣的做法不可能保证永久的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此  我们才必须推翻联邦政府
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论联邦用什么策略  真相都已经呈现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此才让市民们返回地上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为联邦政府会预测不到你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是这样  也不可能让6万市民就此封口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且地面上还有友军和卡塔隆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过这个假情报把舆论引为助力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为开始攻击的布局…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS手里还有什么王牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:13.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台MS…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是Flag？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你一旦得知非洲塔之变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定能在这儿见到你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪开！我没空管你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会吃你这邪道的闭门羹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我来盯住你的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的盟友制造的  这台Masurao的奥义！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有破绽——！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格杀勿论！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只追求纯粹的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有战斗的人生…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与Gundam的战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后超越Gundam！  这就是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存的证明！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以不再这样生存！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！搅局的么！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子的残留量也不多…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再说吧  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我好好记住！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙还活着么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  由你来改变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替没能将这些改变的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  洛克昂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就由我改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我自己改变…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.15,0:22:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队取消了包围网…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事…  部队在两个地方集结
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打算在解救出人质之前动手么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种布阵…大有奥妙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  把非洲塔周围1000米以内的风速资料表示出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.10,0:23:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到轨道电梯坠落情况的部队配置
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…还有一部么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Memento Mori  进入扫射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电力  开始供给
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已开始电力供给
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距充电完成还有  0187
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.07,0:23:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输出功率上限设定为6800
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛乱分子卡塔隆  还有Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.74,0:23:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好承受神雷的制裁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.12,0:24:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪光与破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.65,0:24:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝望与苦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夺取生命的战火中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们的思念交织着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.15,0:24:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「在消散的光之中」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.08,0:24:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在爱转变成恨之前
